function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)

	for i, Player in ipairs(Hydra.ActorsInTriggerBounds(triggerRitualSpaceExt)) do
		if bIsSelfInTrigger == false then
			bIsSelfInTrigger = Hydra.ActorIsPlayer(Player)
		end
	end
	
	if bIsSelfInTrigger == true then
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idSelf, fxVinesAppear)
		Hydra.Wait(2.85)
	end
end
